PARTIAL sum(CASE WHEN (date_dim.d_date >= '1999-04-19'::date) THEN (catalog_sales.cs_sales_price - COALESCE(catalog_returns.cr_refunded_cash, '0'::numeric)) ELSE '0'::numeric END)

Plans.Filter: ((date_dim.d_date >= '1999-03-20 00:00:00'::timestamp without time zone) AND (date_dim.d_date <= '1999-05-19 00:00:00'::timestamp without time zone))

original_sql:
select 
   w_state
  ,i_item_id
  ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1999-04-19' as date))
 		then cs_sales_price - coalesce(cr_refunded_cash,0) else 0 end) as sales_before
  ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1999-04-19' as date))
 		then cs_sales_price - coalesce(cr_refunded_cash,0) else 0 end) as sales_after
 from
   catalog_sales left outer join catalog_returns on
       (cs_order_number = cr_order_number
        and cs_item_sk = cr_item_sk)
  ,warehouse
  ,item
  ,date_dim
 where
 i_item_sk          = cs_item_sk
 and cs_warehouse_sk    = w_warehouse_sk
 and cs_sold_date_sk    = d_date_sk
 and d_date between  (cast ('1999-04-19' as date) - interval '30 day')
                and (cast ('1999-04-19' as date) + interval '30 day') 
 and i_category  = 'Home'
 and i_manager_id between 25 and 64
 and cs_wholesale_cost between 17 and 36
 and cr_reason_sk = 16
 group by
    w_state,i_item_id
 order by w_state,i_item_id
limit 100
